briefdescription.para: Convenience macro to check if errors occurred.

detaileddescription.para: which enables it to be used as an expression: if(TF_HAS_ERRORS(m,expr)) //cope!

briefdescription.para: Report current TfErrorMark instances and the stack traces that created them to stdout for debugging purposes.

detaileddescription.para: To call this function, set _enableTfErrorMarkStackTraces in errorMark.cpp and enable the TF_ERROR_MARK_TRACKING TfDebug code.
